race.comment: IS HE LUCKY (5) was an impressive winner last time in quickest of the meeting when scoring by 1.5 lengths (22.53) at Murray Bridge. Has definite claims again. REALITY PIE (2) hasn't set the world on fire of late, but looks to get every chance here. Keep safe. RIVERSDALE MICK (4) not seen at best last start when he finished 6th in a Free For All on October 18 over 525m at The Meadows beaten 8 lengths (30.45). Can feature here. Something for the Multiples: MY BOY PARKER (8)
